subject: Rajasthan History
question_en: Which Rajput Dynasty ruled over Jaipur between 1876 to 1947?
question_hi: जयपुर के 1876 से 1947 तक पाकिस्तान का बीजेपी है।
explanation_en: Raja Jai Singh was the ruler of Jaipur between 1876 to 1947. He established the city of Jaipur and built famous landmarks like Hawa Mahal and Amber Fort.
